skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
When listened to immediately after waking up, this five minute message sets the tone of your morning so you can be your most productive and present for the rest of the day. 
-Add 5AM Call to your Flash Briefing
-Say, "Alexa, play my Flash Briefing" to listen to the 5AM message.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
